data.description: Discover your dream home at the Paseos of Mission Ridge! This captivating two-story residence boasts a perfect blend of modernism & cleanliness with a pristine feel all around. The master bedroom is a sanctuary of its own, complete with a walk-in closet featuring oversized built-in floating shelving. The master bath pampers you with a double sink granite vanity, a relaxing jetted tub, and a stylish tile walk-in shower. Gourmet kitchen features granite countertops, rich dark brown cabinetry, and sleek stainless steel accents & appliances sitting under a subway tile backsplash w. mosaic stone center accents. The heart of this home is the backyard offering an oasis of privacy with an extended back wall and stamped concrete. Enjoy the serene ambiance under a pergola next to the covered patio, surrounded by lush turf grass and charming corner brick accents. This property is move-in ready and waiting to meet its next owner!
